Package: aletheia
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), tesseract-ocr, poppler-utils
Maintainer: Aletheia Team <team@aletheia.dev>
Description: Document Parser for AI Agents
 Aletheia is a document and image parsing tool designed for
 AI agents like GitHub Copilot. It extracts structured content
 from PDFs, images, and diagrams with semantic understanding.
Homepage: https://github.com/aletheia/aletheia
